&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a dynamic and results-oriented Senior Sales Engineer to partner with our MSP Account Executives in driving new business opportunities, allowing MSPs to protect their customers with managed detections, guided response, and 24/7 security operations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Sales Engineer, you will drive business growth by understanding customer needs, providing technical solutions and effectively articulating the value of our products or services. The ideal candidate possesses broad technical knowledge across various cybersecurity domains, strong communication skills, and a passion for helping organizations resolve complex security challenges.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Sales Engineers serve as the technical bridge between our services and prospective clients, translating business challenges into tailored cybersecurity solutions. This is an exciting opportunity to contribute to our company’s success and be part of a high-performing sales team in a competitive market. If you’re passionate about sales and innovation, we invite you to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Account Executives to effectively communicate the technical value of our cybersecurity consulting services during prospect calls, demos, and presentations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct product demonstrations to showcase key features and functionalities and address technical questions and concerns from customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to sales strategies, pricing decisions and contract negotiations based on technical considerations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience working cross-product domain with tools such as Linux, Windows, AD, logging, firewalls, Microsoft Azure, Amazon Web Services (AWS), Google Cloud, CrowdStrike, VMware Carbon Black, Duo Security, Office365, Okta, and other security tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn about customers&#39; successes and challenges, sharing customer feedback within Blumira, and advocating for customer interests&lt;/li&gt;
